 CellLabel->"Out[6]=",ExpressionUUID->"aefcc003-d5ed-4a44-ab78-8d15aef142de"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
In obtained plot, abcissa values were assigned in situ, according to the \
order of the entered data in the list named (data). The first of these values \
(elements of the list) which may also be interpreted as a vector ( the \
computer name for the one dimensional sequential data) or a set is the \
observed value of the viscosities at the experiment\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.765028096552121*^9, 3.76502850180848*^9}, {
  3.7650322485724063`*^9, 3.7650323061404905`*^9}, {3.765806194489023*^9, 
  3.765806225189438*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"69f4a819-872a-4697-a7be-\
83ade9f349ee"],

Cell["\<\
The observed value of the viscosity in the initial temperature is,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.765029680557223*^9, 3.7650297410643826`*^9}, {
  3.7650323639690976`*^9, 
  3.765032379916609*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"80505cb3-aa99-4635-bd61-\
fd1bf4eff2ac"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"data", "[", 
  RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7650297446553946`*^9, 3.765029758322268*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[7]:=",ExpressionUUID->"9a7cb73f-4e73-44de-bb07-b2b5233b64ad"],

Cell[BoxData["2.16`"], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.765029760535636*^9, 3.765734103955008*^9, 
  3.7658070438974705`*^9, 3.765815254231168*^9, 3.7658166139666414`*^9, 
  3.7658257988635426`*^9, 3.765853245678748*^9, 3.765856271563406*^9, 
  3.765856323578566*^9, 3.7658579160142593`*^9, 3.7658773669371657`*^9, 
  3.7658779912669764`*^9, 3.7660813853539934`*^9, 3.767063564121232*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[7]=",ExpressionUUID->"4a09b8e1-8371-4fbf-98d4-76db843e4926"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["The 9 th. observation is,", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7650297765477896`*^9, 3.7650298183235044`*^9}, 
   3.7650298851169443`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"69cf004c-b7c5-475d-9798-\
7a2b4b1397a1"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"data", "[", 
  RowBox[{"[", "9", "]"}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7650298237022114`*^9, 3.765029830986288*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[8]:=",ExpressionUUID->"82fe6f4a-0fce-47be-8525-f89911f3f5b5"],

Cell[BoxData["28.18`"], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.7650298325370893`*^9, 3.765734103981976*^9, 
  3.765807043923542*^9, 3.765815254256152*^9, 3.7658166139896293`*^9, 
  3.7658257988915267`*^9, 3.765853245694373*^9, 3.7658562715794134`*^9, 
  3.7658563235945582`*^9, 3.7658579160372467`*^9, 3.7658773669541545`*^9, 
  3.7658779912849655`*^9, 3.766081385392984*^9, 3.767063564141229*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[8]=",ExpressionUUID->"ad51da5c-429c-468e-81a6-10b3c8d4ce54"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
We have regular increase in temperature during the experiment, that means we \
can develop a relation calculating the temperatures for each entry of \
viscosity data to experiment list.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7650298495382724`*^9, 3.7650299000366993`*^9}, 
   3.7650299496763177`*^9, {3.7658070669362855`*^9, 3.7658071971616783`*^9}, {
   3.765807240948597*^9, 
   3.765807362096204*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8c723c57-ad0a-4f7d-b885-\
c96b7599f72b"],

Cell["\<\
The first entry is the viscosity at the initial temperature 15 (\[Degree]C)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658073886519904`*^9, 
  3.7658074372991796`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a99d50f5-2a5c-48df-9fc7-\
db97e03b8031"],

Cell["Let us assign n for the index of the viscosity value.", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658075639076023`*^9, 
  3.7658076222521806`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"25fdf8c0-a79f-469a-bd63-\
564f876caed5"],

Cell["\<\
For the first entry point n = 1 and t = 15 (\[Degree]C) = 15 + n-1 = 15 (\
\[Degree]C)  or 15 + 2 (n-1) = 15 + 1 (1-1) = 15 + 0 = 15 (\[Degree]C)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.765807656014841*^9, 3.765807722200325*^9}, {
   3.765807895212202*^9, 3.765807983859103*^9}, {3.765808255517644*^9, 
   3.7658083102540846`*^9}, 
   3.7658084176264153`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"f4c95302-7e57-4b88-992e-\
7b8c17506578"],

Cell["\<\
For the second entry point n = 2 and t = 15 + 2 (\[Degree]C) = 15 + 2 (n-1) = \
15 + 2 (2-1) = 15 + 2 = 17 (\[Degree]C)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658077619355803`*^9, 3.765807788537341*^9}, {
   3.7658080502131095`*^9, 3.765808238964614*^9}, 
   3.7658084562285023`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"2480d870-6a9c-42dc-bf9a-\
ff19609fad66"],

Cell[".....", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658083522396994`*^9, 
  3.765808353007145*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2de09c54-68d7-46ff-ad26-\
54e20a4bc404"],

Cell["\<\
For the ninth entry point n = 9 and t = 15 + 2 (n-1) = 15 + 2 (9-1) = 15 + 2\
\[Times]8 = 15 + 16 = 31 (\[Degree]C)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658077619355803`*^9, 3.765807788537341*^9}, {
  3.7658080502131095`*^9, 3.765808238964614*^9}, {3.7658083637503815`*^9, 
  3.7658084116107655`*^9}, {3.7658084771173944`*^9, 3.7658084873999605`*^9}, {
  3.765808579805138*^9, 
  3.765808603432051*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"65900a39-1fe4-4726-9a42-\
e17216ceac15"],

Cell["\<\
Since the initial temperature and the temrature step are constants, we can \
define a more general relation valid for either different initial temperatues \
and the temperature increase steps. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.765808757866371*^9, 
  3.765808943562086*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e8606648-5d05-4c1d-8c6c-\
dba35681f1f4"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"initialTemp", " ", "=", " ", "15"}], ";", " ", 
  RowBox[{"tempStep", "=", " ", "2"}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658090060618887`*^9, 3.76580901867177*^9}, {
  3.765809072512835*^9, 3.7658091147283063`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[9]:=",ExpressionUUID->"e0237111-a50e-49fc-a1af-21489ced063b"],

Cell["\<\
We can devise a user defined function for this entry point / temperature \
relation. The variable n will be defined as the index (ordinal number) of the \
data set.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658086587930274`*^9, 3.765808719847864*^9}, {
  3.7658244038258553`*^9, 
  3.765824479639349*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a54d1746-b643-49aa-8742-\
5c7a63dc1aeb"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"F", "[", "n_", "]"}], " ", "=", " ", 
  RowBox[{"initialTemp", " ", "+", " ", 
   RowBox[{"tempStep", 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{"n", "-", "1"}], ")"}]}]}]}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.765808730440217*^9, 3.765808745191537*^9}, {
  3.7658091949243126`*^9, 3.7658092747565823`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[10]:=",ExpressionUUID->"e310dbc2-bb1f-491a-b5f4-8dffbf1757c4"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"15", "+", 
  RowBox[{"2", " ", 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"-", "1"}], "+", "n"}], ")"}]}]}]], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.7658092934480667`*^9, 3.765815254314127*^9, 
  3.7658166140346036`*^9, 3.7658257989434977`*^9, 3.765853245725621*^9, 
  3.76585627160839*^9, 3.7658563236205425`*^9, 3.765857916067229*^9, 
  3.765877367009123*^9, 3.7658779913139486`*^9, 3.766081385466941*^9, 
  3.767063564185205*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[10]=",ExpressionUUID->"207f36be-ca0c-499e-8b67-a5114f7438e7"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
We can determine the temperatures for each determined value of viscosity in \
our experiment.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658093108954487`*^9, 3.7658093152423058`*^9}, {
   3.765809390226088*^9, 3.765809457953104*^9}, 
   3.76581569848106*^9},ExpressionUUID->"5de105b6-e983-4d9d-bf59-\
05d18e19daea"],

Cell["\<\
list = Table[iteratedValue , {iterator, initial value of the iterator , end \
value of the iterator , (increase / decrease) value of the iterator}]\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658245604639745`*^9, 3.76582474719985*^9}, {
  3.7658247843915143`*^9, 3.765824805643323*^9}, {3.7658529966998434`*^9, 
  3.765852997872041*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"03bd2d3f-1b78-41c9-bbb5-\
df8e90e7b16d"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"temperature", " ", "=", 
  RowBox[{"Table", "[", 
   RowBox[{"x", ",", " ", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{"x", ",", "initialTemp", ",", 
      RowBox[{"F", "[", 
       RowBox[{"Length", "[", "data", "]"}], "]"}], ",", "tempStep"}], 
     "}"}]}], "]"}]}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658094646512594`*^9, 3.765809554567237*^9}, {
  3.7658096472981787`*^9, 3.7658096621464415`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[11]:=",ExpressionUUID->"77b7162e-6c6b-4fe6-89e0-1d336c596f76"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"{", 
  RowBox[{
  "15", ",", "17", ",", "19", ",", "21", ",", "23", ",", "25", ",", "27", ",",
    "29", ",", "31"}], "}"}]], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.7658095569774942`*^9, 3.7658152543391037`*^9, 
  3.7658166140595884`*^9, 3.7658257989744787`*^9, 3.7658532457412453`*^9, 
  3.7658562716243725`*^9, 3.765856323641531*^9, 3.765857916085219*^9, 
  3.765877367027113*^9, 3.765877991330939*^9, 3.7660813855408936`*^9, 
  3.767063564205201*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[11]=",ExpressionUUID->"a6eba1ed-fe12-4640-8bec-e8b9281026bb"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
Now, we are in position to be able to plot the temperature of each entry \
point :\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658157733193474`*^9, 
