Cell["\<\
Temperaature is changing step by step from the initial to the final stage of \
the experiment. We call this \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]The Viscosity Chart of a \
Given Substance by Discrete Steps of Temperature\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote].\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658158725289955`*^9, 
  3.7658160959638042`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b9e2ea48-882b-4687-b731-\
57c3667f1cd3"],

Cell["\<\
Observed viscosity values are stored in the list \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]data\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] and plotted above as p1. The temperature values of \
these experiment is stored in the list \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]temperature\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] and plotted above as p2. We can plot them side by \
side or in one single plot.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7658161785354357`*^9, 3.7658163045201616`*^9}, 
   3.765824840211492*^9, 3.7658530292662497`*^9, {3.765853069339292*^9, 
