Cell["\<\
In  Mathematica there is more than a one way to achieve things. But for even \
publication quality, these examples may suit some needs. All the graphs is \
customisable for any data and any choice. Mathematica has many other tweaks \
for plottting anything, these examples are the simplest show-up for scatter \
plots. \
\>", "Text",
